title: HOUR 3- Duncan Robinson and Kevin Nealon Sep 18, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Duncan Robinson and Kevin Nealon Sep 18, 2020
description:
Duncan Robinson tell Dan how excited he is to win game two and he is looking forward to game 3. Duncan says "Grit" is the word he would use to describe his Miami Heat team. Dan talked to Kevin Nealon about his SNL days.
